OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FThe Court of Appeal has rejected a bid
OL,8,Fto increase the sentences of a couple
OL,9,Fwho were jailed for life for murdering
OL,10,Ftheir two-year-old grandson.
OL,12,FEthan Ives-Griffiths was subjected to
OL,13,Fweeks of abuse at the hands of Michael
OL,14,FIves, and his wife Kerry Ives.
OL,16,FThe toddler was extremely dehydrated
OL,17,Fand severely underweight, with visible
OL,18,Fmarks and bruises, when he collapsed
OL,19,Fwith a catastrophic head injury at his
OL,20,Fgrandparents' home in Deeside,
OL,21,FFlintshire, in August 2021.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
