OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FIn October last year, the couple were
OL,8,Fjailed for life at Mold Crown Court.
OL,9,FMichael Ives was sentenced to a
OL,10,Fminimum of 23 years' imprisonment, and
OL,11,FKerry Ives for a minimum of 17 years.
OL,13,FEthan's mother, Shannon Ives, who had
OL,14,Fbeen staying with her son at her
OL,15,Fparents' home, was also found guilty
OL,16,Fof causing or allowing his death and
OL,17,Fof child cruelty, and was sentenced to
OL,18,F12 years in prison.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FOn Thursday, 12 March, Bill Emlyn
OL,8,FJones KC, for the Solicitor General,
OL,9,Fasked the Court of Appeal in London to
OL,10,Fincrease the grandparents' sentences,
OL,11,Fsaying they were "unduly lenient".
OL,13,FBut Lord Justice Popplewell, Mr
OL,14,FJustice Sweeting and Judge Penelope
OL,15,FMoreland ruled that the sentences were
OL,16,Fappropriate and should not be
OL,17,Fincreased.
OL,26,@sD@ROUsD@aO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FReading the judgment, Lord Justice
OL,8,FPopplewell said Ethan was a "brave"
OL,9,Fand "resilient" boy with a "strong
OL,10,Fcharacter" and that his grandparents
OL,11,F"did not like him standing up for
OL,12,Fhimself".
OL,14,FSetting out some of the facts of the
OL,15,Foffending, he added that CCTV showed
OL,16,FMichael Ives carrying his grandson by
OL,17,Fthe top of his arm and appearing to
OL,18,Fpunch him after putting him into a car
OL,19,Fseat.
OL,26,@pD@]OUpD@cO]qD@EOUqD@OO]qD@\OUrD@JO]sD@
OL,26,AAOUtD@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
