OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FOther footage showed the boy in the
OL,8,Fback garden "walking with a peculiar,
OL,9,Fwide stance and an uncertain gait",
OL,10,Fwhich could be linked to the early
OL,11,Feffects of brain injuries caused by
OL,12,Fprevious blows to his head, the judge
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FTo humiliate Ethan, Michael would make
OL,16,Fhim stand with his hands on his head,
OL,17,Fhe added.
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@bO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/16
