OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FHe continued: "He says that when
OL,8,Fsentencing for the murder the judge
OL,9,Fcould not divorce the aggravating
OL,10,Ffactors of the murder from the factors
OL,11,Fof what had gone before."
OL,13,FThe judge added: "In Michael's case,
OL,14,Fwe are not persuaded that the sentence
OL,15,Fwas unduly lenient."
OL,17,FHe also said that it was clear that
OL,18,Fthe sentencing judge, Mr Justice
OL,19,FGriffiths, had the overall position
OL,20,F"clearly" in mind.
OL,26,@oD@OOUsD@YO]uD@ROUwD@TO]|D@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/16
