CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FThe judge said that the panel was also
OL,8,F"unpersuaded" in Kerry's case that the
OL,9,Fminimum term was unduly lenient.
OL,11,F"The judge was very well placed to
OL,12,Fassess her culpability and personal
OL,13,Fmitigation," Lord Justice Popplewell
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FAs for Shannon Ives, Gordon Cole KC,
OL,17,Frepresenting her, appealed against her
OL,18,Fsentence, telling the court the jail
OL,19,Fterm was "too long" and that the judge
OL,20,Fhad not fully taken into account her
OL,21,Fpersonal mitigation.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]sD@AOUuD@LO]{D@JOU{D@SO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
