PN,46309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FLord Justice Popplewell said the
OL,8,Fjudges had given careful consideration
OL,9,Fto his arguments but were unpersuaded
OL,10,Fthat they justified "interfering with
OL,11,Fthe sentence".
OL,13,FDuring the sentencing of the trio in
OL,14,FOctober 2025, Mr Justice Griffiths
OL,15,Fsaid: "Ethan Ives-Griffiths was a two-
OL,16,Fyear-old with an independent spirit.
OL,17,FHis mother and his grandparents hit
OL,18,Fhim, but when they did, he was defiant
OL,19,Fand even laughed.
OL,26,@rD@UOUsD@MO]wD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
