CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,F"Even though he was only a toddler, he
OL,8,Fwas a brave and resilient boy with a
OL,9,Fstrong character. He already had
OL,10,Fqualities which in an adult could make
OL,11,Ffor greatness, but the people hitting
OL,12,Fhim didn't like the little boy
OL,13,Fstanding up for himself. They decided
OL,14,Fto break him."
OL,16,FThe judge said Shannon Ives knew her
OL,17,Fparents were violent as she had
OL,18,Fsuffered at their hands while growing
OL,19,Fup.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/16
