OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FShannon Ives' parents accused her of
OL,8,Fhitting her son during the trial, with
OL,9,FMichael Ives telling the jury his
OL,10,Fdaughter was "quick-tempered" and
OL,11,Fwould slap Ethan a couple of times a
OL,12,Fday, but Shannon Ives told told the
OL,13,Fjury her parents were "horrible" and
OL,14,Fabused her as a child.
OL,16,F"Shannon knew Ethan was not safe with
OL,17,Fher parents. She gave evidence that
OL,18,Fshe saw both of them hit Ethan," he
OL,19,Fsaid. "She didn't tell social
OL,20,Fservices, she covered up what was
OL,21,Fbeing done. She was complicit in it.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@]O]uD@WOUuD@`O]xD@AOUzD@`O]{D@
OL,26,AGOU
