SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,F"She knew that Ethan was emaciated,
OL,8,Fbruised all over his body and had
OL,9,Frecent injuries on his face. She knew
OL,10,Fthat he was painfully thin,
OL,11,Fmalnourished, and dehydrated.
OL,13,F"She knew that Michael was violent and
OL,14,Fwas being systematically cruel and
OL,15,Fphysically abusive towards Ethan. She
OL,16,Fknew that Ethan could no longer walk
OL,17,For talk as he had walked and talked
OL,18,Fbefore. She did not cause his death
OL,19,Fbut she was active in allowing it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/16
