OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FWhen Ethan was examined by doctors
OL,8,Fafter his death, he was found to have
OL,9,Fabdominal injuries likely to have been
OL,10,Fcaused by blows in the days before his
OL,11,Fcollapse. Other injuries included
OL,12,Fbruises which were consistent with
OL,13,Fgrip marks on his leg and face.
OL,15,FExperts said Ethan would have died of
OL,16,Fdehydration within days had he not
OL,17,Fsuffered the head injury, and at the
OL,18,Ftime of his death, he weighed just
OL,19,F10kg, the court was told.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
