SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FThe jury heard medical evidence that
OL,8,FEthan's fatal head injury was caused
OL,9,Fby deliberate force or shaking and
OL,10,Foccurred at the time, or in the
OL,11,Fminutes before, he collapsed on the
OL,12,Fevening of August 14, 2021. Ethan was
OL,13,Ftaken to the Countess of Chester
OL,14,FHospital and later transferred to
OL,15,FAlder Hey Children's Hospital in
OL,16,FLiverpool, where he died two days
OL,17,Flater.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/16
