OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,FIn a previous victim personal
OL,8,Fstatement, Ethan's father William
OL,9,FGriffiths said he would never come to
OL,10,Fterms with what happened to his son.
OL,12,F"I feel angry that he was taken away
OL,13,Ffrom me and placed with his
OL,14,Fgrandparents, who then subjected him
OL,15,Fto cruel behaviour, denying him food
OL,16,For basic comforts, regularly being
OL,17,Fmean and nasty towards him and
OL,18,Fexcluding and disciplining him for no
OL,19,Freason," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773414686
OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects bid to
OL,4,Cincrease sentence of couple who
OL,5,Cmurdered grandson
OL,7,F"He must have felt so sad and alone
OL,8,Fand I feel sad that this is what his
OL,9,Flast few weeks on this earth were
OL,10,Flike. No child should be subjected to
OL,11,Fthis behaviour by anyone, let alone
OL,12,Fpeople that should have loved and
OL,13,Fcared for him.
OL,15,F"Ethan has been a huge loss to our
OL,16,Flives and leaves a void that can never
OL,17,Fbe replaced for anyone who met and
OL,18,Floved him."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@KO]
